tiles.name: User Sessions Query
tiles.query: select AVG(duration) AS " " from useraction where usersession.userType = "SYNTHETIC"

tiles.name: User Sessions Query
tiles.query: select count(*) as "Erreurs HTTP & JavaScript"  from useraction where javaScriptErrorCount >=1 or requestErrorCount  >=1 and usersession.userType = "SYNTHETIC"

tiles.name: User Sessions Query
tiles.query: select COUNT(DISTINCT city) AS "Villes" from usersession where userType = "SYNTHETIC"

tiles.name: User Sessions Query
tiles.query: SELECT apdexCategory, COUNT(*) AS "Tests"  FROM useraction where usersession.userType="SYNTHETIC" GROUP BY apdexCategory ORDER BY  count(*) DESC

tiles.name: User Sessions Query
tiles.query: SELECT  domain, top (useraction.name, 5) AS "Name", apdexCategory, COUNT(*) AS "Count"  FROM useraction where usersession.userType="SYNTHETIC" GROUP BY apdexCategory, domain ORDER BY  count(*) DESC
